# Pydantic-settings reads from process env, not from this directory's .env.
# The canonical env template lives at ../.env.example. Copy it to ../.env
# at the repo root; the backend picks up vars from the shell environment
# regardless of cwd.
#
# Variables documented in ../.env.example:
#   - Provider API keys: OPENAI_API_KEY, ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, XAI_API_KEY,
#     OPENROUTER_API_KEY
#   - Backend overrides: LOOM_HOME, LOOM_ACTIVE_VAULT,
#     LOOM_DEFAULT_PROVIDER, LOOM_CORS_ORIGINS
